data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 1-bathroom home situated in the heart of Ashland. This lovely abode boasts a brand-new water heater, a recently replaced roof, fresh vinyl siding, newer windows, and waterproof LVP flooring in the kitchen, bathroom, dining room, and bedroom. The updated kitchen is equipped with gleaming stainless steel appliances, making it a delight for any home.  Step into the spacious living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones. These inviting spaces seamlessly flow to the outdoors, where you can enjoy two decks—one at the front and one at the back of the house—providing ample opportunities to soak in the fresh air and admire the surroundings.  This wonderful home also features a two-stall detached garage, offering convenient off-street parking and easy alley access. Don't miss out on the chance to make this move-in-ready gem your own!
